{"id": "1386821238076346460", "channel_id": "1386821238076346460", "type": 0, "author_id": "263881468667887616", "author_name": "theandykat", "author_bot": false, "content": "Wheel Unseen describes conceal incorrectly when viewed from collection. It falsely states that conceal has a maximum of 3 stacks. In a battle, conceal has an accurate description, maximum stacks 5.\nDerison of Destiny says it will give extra charge for each dead enemy, but in battle it instead gives charge for each dead ally.", "timestamp": "2025-06-23T21:32:29.050000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1386821238437052517", "filename": "Screenshot_20250623_142122_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 127588, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1386821238076346460/1386821238437052517/Screenshot_20250623_142122_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cc3d6d&is=69caebed&hm=d9f194a7c8242fffd0d1639a27ffb6812bda5892a8697a585641b63b532a0154&"}, {"id": "1386821238986637332", "filename": "Screenshot_20250623_142916_Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 141050, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1386821238076346460/1386821238986637332/Screenshot_20250623_142916_Morimens.jpg?ex=69cc3d6d&is=69caebed&hm=079d0b81053b4295965c1ebc08ed31ef3ccf947d662058780e9508ae06cfa6b3&"}, {"id": "1386821239343157258", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20250623_143021_Morimens.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 4262318, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1386821238076346460/1386821239343157258/Screen_Recording_20250623_143021_Morimens.mp4?ex=69cc3d6d&is=69caebed&hm=194b73c38200b5692dd23943141566ea1e4fa3eac496e85decb159d70ccec208&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1386821238076346460", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Traphase inaccurate descriptions for Derison of Destiny and Wheel Unseen (Conceal)", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420